+ Understand Lakeflow\nDeclarative Pipelines for Ingestion
++ Declarative Framework
+++_ Define WHAT, not HOW
+++_ SQL or Python source files
+++_ Automatic orchestration & retries
++ Streaming Tables
+++_ Delta tables with streaming support
+++_ Exactly-once processing
+++_ Append-only ingestion workloads
-- Benefits
---_ Auto orchestration & parallelism
---_ Transient failure retries
---_ Incremental processing only
---_ Schema management built-in
-- Pipeline Execution
---_ Source files: transformations folder
---_ Pipeline handles checkpoints internally
---_ View execution in Pipeline Editor (DAG)
